query.tSql: SELECT TOP(30) [cr4a3_productid], cr4a3_productname, cr4a3_productprice AS [price], [cr4a3_primaryimageurl] AS [primaryimageurl], [cr4a3_maximumvariantprice] AS [maxvariantprice], [cr4a3_minimumvariantprice] AS [minvariantprice], [createdon] AS [created_on], [cr4a3_productdescription] AS [description], [cr4a3_productnumber] AS [productnumber], [cr4a3_productitemid] AS [itemid] FROM cr4a3_product WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE [ownerid] = 'a7d8249f-c55f-f011-bec2-000d3a35b168' AND [statecode] = 0 AND cr4a3_productprice <= 1199;
query.fetchXml: <fetch count="30" mapping="logical" no-lock="true"><entity name="cr4a3_product"><attribute name="cr4a3_productid" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productname" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productprice" alias="price" /><attribute name="cr4a3_primaryimageurl" alias="primaryimageurl" /><attribute name="cr4a3_maximumvariantprice" alias="maxvariantprice" /><attribute name="cr4a3_minimumvariantprice" alias="minvariantprice" /><attribute name="createdon" alias="created_on" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productdescription" alias="description" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productnumber" alias="productnumber" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productitemid" alias="itemid" /><filter type="and"><condition attribute="ownerid" operator="eq-userid" /><condition attribute="statecode" operator="eq" value="0" /><condition attribute="cr4a3_productprice" operator="le" value="1199" /></filter></entity></fetch>
query.explanation:
Explanation: The query lists up to 30 active products from the **cr4a3_product** table owned by the current user, with a price less than or equal to $1199. It shows product details like name, price, description, and images to help find bike options within the budget.

Rephrased Question: Budget $1199 for bike - what are my options?

result.description: The Wadenmos running shoe is a recommended choice for neutral runners who want a soft, flexible everyday trainer with a great fit. result.description: The Jaserly Pants for women are made from a woven 4-way recycled polyester. Design features of this stretchy style include moisture-wicking properties, front patch pockets, an elastic waistband.

Dry, lightweight and flexible, the women's tall Darow pants are built to excel on the trail. These pants offer lefthand zip pocket which doubles as a storage pouch, and with their windproof and waterproof features makes them perfect pants for hiking.

test_case_context.question: I need good footwear within $19-$28 price range.

query.tSql: SELECT TOP(30) [cr4a3_productid], cr4a3_productname, cr4a3_productprice AS [price], [cr4a3_maximumvariantprice] AS [maxvariantprice], [cr4a3_productnumber] AS [productnumber], [cr4a3_minimumvariantprice] AS [minvariantprice], [cr4a3_productdescription] AS [description], [cr4a3_productitemid] AS [itemid], [cr4a3_totalratings] AS [totalratings], [createdon] AS [created_on] FROM cr4a3_product WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE cr4a3_productprice BETWEEN 19 AND 28 AND cr4a3_productname LIKE 'footwear%' AND [statecode] = 0;
query.fetchXml: <fetch count="30" mapping="logical" no-lock="true"><entity name="cr4a3_product"><attribute name="cr4a3_productid" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productname" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productprice" alias="price" /><attribute name="cr4a3_maximumvariantprice" alias="maxvariantprice" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productnumber" alias="productnumber" /><attribute name="cr4a3_minimumvariantprice" alias="minvariantprice" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productdescription" alias="description" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productitemid" alias="itemid" /><attribute name="cr4a3_totalratings" alias="totalratings" /><attribute name="createdon" alias="created_on" /><filter type="and"><condition attribute="cr4a3_productprice" operator="ge" value="19" /><condition attribute="cr4a3_productprice" operator="le" value="28" /><condition attribute="cr4a3_productname" operator="like" value="footwear%" /><condition attribute="statecode" operator="eq" value="0" /></filter></entity></fetch>

Explanation: The query retrieves details like **Name**, **Price**, **Description**, and **TotalRatings** from the **Product** table for active products (**Status** = 0) whose **Name** starts with 'footwear' and whose **Price** is between $19 and $28.

query.tSql: SELECT TOP(30) [cr4a3_productid], cr4a3_productname, cr4a3_productprice AS [price], cr4a3_baseprice AS [baseprice], cr4a3_totalratings AS [totalratings], [cr4a3_productdescription] AS [description], [cr4a3_primaryimageurl] AS [primaryimageurl], [cr4a3_masterproductid] AS [masterproductid], [createdon] AS [created_on], [cr4a3_productitemid] AS [itemid] FROM cr4a3_product WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE [statecode] = 0 ORDER BY cr4a3_productname;
query.fetchXml: <fetch count="30" mapping="logical" no-lock="true"><entity name="cr4a3_product"><attribute name="cr4a3_productid" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productname" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productprice" alias="price" /><attribute name="cr4a3_baseprice" alias="baseprice" /><attribute name="cr4a3_totalratings" alias="totalratings" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productdescription" alias="description" /><attribute name="cr4a3_primaryimageurl" alias="primaryimageurl" /><attribute name="cr4a3_masterproductid" alias="masterproductid" /><attribute name="createdon" alias="created_on" /><attribute name="cr4a3_productitemid" alias="itemid" /><filter type="and"><condition attribute="statecode" operator="eq" value="0" /></filter><order attribute="cr4a3_productname" /></entity></fetch>
query.explanation:
Explanation: The query lists active products from the **Product** table, showing details like **Name**, **Price**, **BasePrice**, **TotalRatings**, and **Description**. It orders the results alphabetically by **Name** to help compare the Pratuma Solo Paddle Board with other accessory options.
